#. type: Plain text
#: docs/version-1.30/modules/en/pages/quick-start.adoc:175
msgid ""
"The `kubewarden-controller` manages a {short-project-name} `PolicyServer`. "
"You can deploy multiple {policy-server}s in the same Kubernetes cluster."
msgstr "El `kubewarden-controller` gestiona un `PolicyServer` de {short-project-name}. Puede desplegar múltiples {policy-server}s en el mismo clúster de Kubernetes."

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/version-1.30/modules/en/pages/quick-start.adoc:178
msgid ""
"A `PolicyServer` validates incoming requests by executing {short-project-"
